<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm Heydenab</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt wegen der Gefangennahme des Heinrich Gebelscheu bei Reichertshofen, dass er Bürger zu Nürnberg ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_59" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l12">VVilhelm Heydnaber </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l13"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dinſt beuor . Lieber vvılhelm . Vns hat fürbraht Dorothe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l14">des <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Gebelſchewh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> elıche <expan>vvirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvie Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jre<ex>n</ex></expan> wirt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l15">bey Reẏkerſhofen <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd Jn v̈mb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvıder ledig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l16">gelaſſen habt / Alſo ob . vvir euch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreẏb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ Er vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l17">Alſo tun vvir euch cʒu vviſſen . daʒ derſelb <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Gebelſchewh </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l18">vnſer Burger iſt / vnd vvo vvir ew auch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l19"><expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> möhten das teten vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn dıe <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> dyoniſij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_59" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm Heydnaber </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dinst bevor. Lieber
                                                Wilhelm, uns hat fürbraht Dorothe, des
                                                  <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Gebelschewh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eliche
                                                  <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie ir
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> wirt bey Reykershofen
                                                  <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> und in ümb
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> wider ledig gelassen
                                                habt, also ob wir euch
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreyb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz
                                                er unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sey. Also
                                                tun wir euch czu wissen, daz derselb
                                                  <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Gebelschewh unser
                                                burger ist. Und wo wir ew auch lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft
                                                  <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> möhten das teten
                                                wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                                  <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                                                dyonisii.</ab>
</div>
